data.description: Desirable Woodstock / Mt. Scott-Arleta Neighborhood! Hard to Find 100 x 100 Lot w/ Wonderful Street Frontage! (Zoned R2.5) Plat shows historical division "blue line." Well maintained Mid Century 1950's One Level Ranch Style Home w/ Basement.  Flowing Floor Plan, Perfect for Entertaining. 2 Generous Bedrooms + Den. Wood Burning Fireplace. Covered Front and Back Porches. Partially Finished Basement for More Possibilities! Fenced Large Backyard w/ Covered Patio. Detached Garage & Off-Street Parking. This Home is Ready for Your Personal Touch! HES:8
